    java.io.Serializable

    public class Courses
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Courses class is used to create a new course. This class also has the information about class timings of that particular course and respective venue of the class.

        Parameters:
        m - A string that contains information that whether course is a mandatory course or an elective
        name - A string that has course name
        code - A string that has course code
        i - A string that knows about the instructor
        acry - A string that stores course acronym
        credits - A string that has course credits
        pre - An ArrayList of type string that has course pre conditions
        post - An ArrayList of type string that has course post conditions
